Ford Motor Credit Company LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 2:06 PM ET
Consumer Finance

Company Overview of Ford Motor Credit Company LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ford Motor Credit Company LLC, through its subsidiaries, provides various automotive financing products to and through automotive dealers worldwide. It offers retail financing products, such as retail installment sale contracts for new and used vehicles; and direct financing leases for new vehicles to retail and commercial customers, including leasing companies, government entities, daily rental companies, and fleet customers. The company also provides wholesale loans to dealers to finance the purchase of vehicle inventory; to finance working capital and improvements to dealership facilities; to finance the purchase of dealership real estate; and to finance other dealer vehicle programs. In ...
Ford Motor Credit Company LLC, through its subsidiaries, provides various automotive financing products to and through automotive dealers worldwide. It offers retail financing products, such as retail installment sale contracts for new and used vehicles; and direct financing leases for new vehicles to retail and commercial customers, including leasing companies, government entities, daily rental companies, and fleet customers. The company also provides wholesale loans to dealers to finance the purchase of vehicle inventory; to finance working capital and improvements to dealership facilities; to finance the purchase of dealership real estate; and to finance other dealer vehicle programs. In addition, it offers various insurance products and services, including physical damage insurance coverage for vehicles at dealer locations and vehicles in transit between final assembly plants and dealer locations; and contractual liability insurance on extended service contracts, commercial automobile and general liability insurance, and surety bonds. Further, the company provides Ford-branded insurance products that are underwritten by non-affiliated insurance companies. The company was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Dearborn, Michigan. Ford Motor Credit Company LLC is a subsidiary of Ford Holdings LLC.
Detailed Description


