Ford Motor Credit Co. LLC


                  Ford Motor Credit Co. LLC is an automotive finance company. It provides dealer and customer finance to support the sale of Ford Motor Co. products. Its primary business is to finance Ford vehicles and supporting Ford's dealers. It offers automotive financing products to and through automotive dealers. The firm operates its business through two segments: Consumer and Non-Consumer. Consumer segment engages in products offering to individuals and businesses that finance the acquisition of vehicles from dealers for personal and commercial use. Non-Consumer segment engages primarily to products offered to automotive dealers, like loans to dealers to finance the purchase of vehicle inventory, improvements to dealership facilities, working capital, and the purchase of dealership real estate. The company was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Dearborn, MI.                





